tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE MusicLibrary ( 
  music_id INT, 
  title VARCHAR(255), 
  composer VARCHAR(255), 
  genre VARCHAR(50), 
  year_released INT, 
  primary key (music_id) 
)

CREATE TABLE sheet_music (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255),
    composer VARCHAR(255),
    genre VARCHAR(50),
    year_published INT
);

CREATE TABLE recordings (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255),
    artist VARCHAR(255),
    album VARCHAR(255),
    duration_minutes INT
);

CREATE TABLE sheet_music (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    title TEXT,
    composer TEXT,
    instrument TEXT,
    genre TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE recordings (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    title TEXT,
    artist TEXT,
    release_date DATE,
    duration TIME
);

CREATE TABLE sheet_music (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255),
    composer VARCHAR(255),
    genre VARCHAR(50),
    year_published INT
);

CREATE TABLE recordings (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255),
    artist VARCHAR(255),
    duration INT,
    format VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE composers (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    nationality VARCHAR(50),
    birth_year INT,
    death_year INT
);

CREATE TABLE sheet_music (
    sheet_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    composer VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    publication_year INT,
    genre VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE recordings (
    recording_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    artist VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    release_year INT,
    genre VARCHAR(100)
);
